data.title: New In Town.
data.text:
Welcome to the neighborhood, "Mozzarella Fella's"!
I must say that they are off to a, "Good Start"!
Today was the perfect time to try out the "New One in Town".
My husband had had Laser Surgery on his eye at Sakowitz Eye Center. This is why I thought of Mozzarella Fella's, quick & on my way home.
 I just had to stop and check them out. I was greeted by, Tammy, who was very friendly and explained and answered all my questions. 
Then Tammy took my order, 1 Meatball Parmesan Hero, 1 Chicken Parmesan Hero and an order of Mozzarella Fella's Garlic Rolls (6), that Tammy had suggested.
We returned home and enjoyed every BITE! Keep up the "Good" job. See you soon!
Dr. Martin & Mrs. Kathryn Steinbaum
